sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KServeSvc as KServe Service<br/>(ClusterIP)
    participant VllmHTTP as vllm-spyre HTTP<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant VllmGRPC as vllm-spyre gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant Spyre as IBM Spyre<br/>Accelerator
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(S3/PVC)
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Engine,S3: Model Loading (Startup)
    Engine->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ (S3)<br/>or filesystem (PVC)
    S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>HFHub: Download tokenizer config (optional)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    HFHub-->>Engine: Tokenizer files

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform-managed)
    Gateway->>KServeSvc: Forward request<br/>Platform-managed routing
    KServeSvc->>VllmHTTP: HTTP/8000<br/>No encryption (pod-internal)
    VllmHTTP->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>Spyre: Accelerated compute<br/>PCIe/device driver
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>VllmHTTP: Generated tokens
    VllmHTTP-->>KServeSvc: JSON response
    KServeSvc-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over KServeSvc,Spyre: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference
    KServeSvc->>VllmGRPC: gRPC/8033<br/>No encryption (pod-internal)
    VllmGRPC->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>Spyre: Accelerated compute<br/>PCIe/device driver
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>VllmGRPC: Generation response
    VllmGRPC-->>KServeSvc: gRPC response
